{"tid":2348634,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla 車又出事…","createTime":"2021-01-01T01:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T07:04:01.000Z","uid":275872,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fa1bfd8b1a09bf786db278493f9681ea85301b","tid":2348634,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T01:06:44.000Z","msg":"Tesla電動車｜博客撰文爆上海廠為追產量犧牲質素 Tesla：擬提出起訴<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201231/OBYW56VD2FCJTC6A2SENEXDFCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201231%2FOBYW56VD2FCJTC6A2SENEXDFCQ%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=a246ed56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201231%2FOBYW56VD2FCJTC6A2SENEXDFCQ%2F&h=65466ba9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201231/OBYW56VD2FCJTC6A2SENEXDFCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n電動車Tesla在內地又出事，今次涉事為一輛Model 3。浙江杭州昨日一輛Tesla Model 3，從溫德姆酒店對面的停車場開出後，隨即撞入該酒店大堂。<br />\n<br />\n今年以來，內地發生多宗Tesla「意外加速」意外。12月12日，在北京市海淀區一輛Tesla Model S突然失控，以時速80公里撞向居民；8月12日，浙江溫州一輛Tesla　Model 3失控沖向停車場攔截桿，連撞多車後再側翻；8月9日，上海一輛Tesla Model 3突然失控衝入油站。海外亦曾發生Tesla意外，12月9日，南韓首爾一輛Tesla Model X在一住宅停車場內突然撞牆起火，導致車內一人死亡、兩人受傷。"},{"pid":"0104fa6c9e4fad306670101aa99047fe9d8f1502","tid":2348634,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"都幾危險"},{"pid":"5b9591a93682e40d2a5ba89397bbdcb7f81e7918","tid":2348634,"uid":330057,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T01:08:34.000Z","msg":"用支那抵撚死<br />\n買車真係絕對唔會買電動輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fd8f5b7cec685e3eeacf378b493637401d63c2","tid":2348634,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b9591a93682e40d2a5ba89397bbdcb7f81e7918","tid":2348634,"uid":330057,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T01:08:34.000Z","msg":"用支那抵撚死<br />\n買車真係絕對唔會買電動輪椅<img src=\"/assets/f